{"tid":704691,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"點解咁多人覺得C朗>美斯","createTime":"2018-06-16T14:57:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-17T01:52:12.000Z","uid":108120,"like":119,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"25de695eff7979c75f8b93ae3c80a4aac4ba574d","tid":704691,"uid":108120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T14:57:23.000Z","msg":"就係困境既時候 C朗同美斯態度差天共地<br />\n球隊落後既時候 C朗一次又一次咁激勵隊友 除左令成隊人人跑多步 自己都多次挺身而出拯救球隊 例如16年對匈牙利 睇佢踢波從來冇比人感覺過佢想放棄 呢種態度令係電視面前睇波既觀眾都被佢感染<br />\n<br />\n美斯踢波係好好睇 令人驚歎 但逆境既時候態度真係輸哂 冇C朗果份感染力 凝聚力 成場波越踢越迷失 自己有自己踢 成隊波又要念在佢係美斯要交個波比佢做 足球踢11個人 係團隊既運動 作為隊長又激勵唔到團隊士氣 攞住個波一個人係咁舞黎舞去 幾勁都唔係下下都咁神奇啦"},{"pid":"5d5eb8d39cc8c3b128da679899b62dead86e040d","tid":704691,"uid":84908,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T14:58:02.000Z","msg":"小花<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e2ec79f444fb877204160605d764e4f8a5db496","tid":704691,"uid":34571,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T14:58:11.000Z","msg":"睇完今場真係要認同"},{"pid":"4b91f9191e2ec0eee2cfcc5a8354ebea67f014f4","tid":704691,"uid":40938,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T14:59:01.000Z","msg":"陣間又屈9你盲反架喇"},{"pid":"ec2ab213b113385461d0277899d1205bb7ae3c89","tid":704691,"uid":90422,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T14:59:05.000Z","msg":"認同<br />\n利申 花迷<br />\n潛水先"},{"pid":"34b0f61d179c0561cc20809e3b907daa5c6ebee0","tid":704691,"uid":43061,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T14:59:18.000Z","msg":"和緊都dup晒頭<br />\n尋日牙朗落後緊都仲有火"},{"pid":"51f63d855b93c60012d0410e30f0f6debb491a11","tid":704691,"uid":60479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T15:0